                  oh there are many other ways of making money, that is true.  But to me it seems that it is revolving around the crafters fully.  And that is where I think it is going to become &quot;this is the price because I can&quot; line coming from the mouth of the crafters is all.<br />
<br />
1- yeah sell decons to them for probably 10-20 gold each.  sell raw resources to them for 10-20 gold each ( rare and ultra rare that is )<br />
<br />
2- grind human mobs for 10-20 silver each<br />
<br />
I am not saying that everyone farms gear for cash, but yes a lot do.<br />
<br />
Lastly, I do agree with what you are saying about the mechanics, and why is it that we are getting fluff patches when we need a huge gain on the preformance of the game.  <br />
<br />
Stop the crashes, stop the loop holes that allow the exploits ( I know easier said then done ) but get down to the root cause of things that are causing the problems in game.<br />
<br />
